cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
title: "GenAction: A Cost-Aware Create-or-Reuse Decision Agent for LLM Response Systems"
abstract: >-
  A research prototype for online create-or-reuse decision making with a
  generative (growing) action set: at each round an agent reuses a stored
  response (cheap, risks a mismatch) or pays a fixed cost to create a new,
  reusable response. Implements naive, cost-aware-threshold, and a
  confidence-bound (LCB/UCB) "doubly optimistic" policy, with experiments, an
  ablation, and a regime study characterising when optimism pays off.
type: software
